            "text": "We’ve had our 600 lux mattress for four weeks now and it’s blissfully comfortable. We had a memory foam mattress before and spent a lot of money on it.I was experiencing problems with my thoracic spine and would be shifting around all through the night to alleviate pain.From the first night the difference was really noticeable and now after four weeks I have no issues at all. Going to bed is a joy. Wish I’d bought it sooner.",
