    "1656583538537cad66": {
      "type": "custom--seo--content",
      "settings": {
        "seo-title": "<h2>Better Sleep, Backed by Science (and 100,000+ Happy Customers)\n</h2>",
        "short-desc": "<p>Sleep isn’t just rest, it’s recovery. That’s why every REM-Fit product is designed to help you fall asleep faster, stay asleep longer, and wake up ready to take on the day.</p>",
        "read-more-content": "<p><strong>Hybrid & Elite Mattresses</strong></p><p>Looking for pressure relief without losing support? Our <a href=\"https://www.rem-fit.co.uk/collections/rem-fit-hybrid-mattresses\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">Hybrid mattresses</span></a> combine breathable memory foam with thousands of pocket springs to keep your spine aligned and your body cool. Want the ultimate upgrade? The <a href=\"https://www.rem-fit.co.uk/collections/elite-hybrid-mattresses\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">Elite range</span></a> takes it further with advanced cooling layers and zoned support, built for deep, uninterrupted sleep.</p><p><strong>Toppers & Protectors</strong></p><p>Not ready to change your mattress? Add instant comfort with a <a href=\"https://www.rem-fit.co.uk/products/rem-fit-halo-topper\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">luxury mattress topper</span></a>, or keep your sleep space fresh with our <a href=\"https://www.rem-fit.co.uk/collections/rem-fit-mattress-protectors\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">waterproof protectors</span></a>, ideal for extending the life of your mattress and pillows.</p><p><strong>Hybrid & Cooling Pillows</strong></p><p>Neck pain? Restless nights? Our <a href=\"https://www.rem-fit.co.uk/collections/rem-fit-pillows\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">Hybrid pillows</span></a> adjust to your shape while keeping their structure night after night. And if you run hot, our <a href=\"https://www.rem-fit.co.uk/products/rem-fit-500-cool-gel-pillow\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">cooling gel pillows</span></a> regulate temperature so you don’t wake up tossing the covers off at 3 am.<br/><strong>Bed Frames & Kids Mattresses</strong></p><p>Build the perfect sleep setup with a durable <a href=\"https://www.rem-fit.co.uk/products/rem-fit-luxe-unity-bed-frame\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">bed frame</span></a> or <a href=\"https://www.rem-fit.co.uk/products/rem-fit-divan-base\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">divan</span></a>, or give your little ones the same support you enjoy with our <a href=\"https://www.rem-fit.co.uk/products/rem-fit-remy-kidz-mattress\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">kids’ mattress collection</span></a>.</p><p><strong>Why choose REM-Fit?</strong> </p><p>Every order includes free next-day delivery, a 200-night trial, and a 15-year guarantee. No risk, just better sleep.</p>"
      }
    },
