            "html": "<div style=\"background:#f8f5fb;padding:36px 0 40px;overflow:hidden;width:100%;\">\n \n  <div style=\"padding:0 20px;text-align:center;margin-bottom:24px;\">\n    <span style=\"display:inline-block;font-size:11px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:0.08em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#3f2155;background:#f0ebf5;padding:4px 10px;border-radius:4px;margin-bottom:10px;\">Original research</span>\n    <h2 style=\"font-size:18px;font-weight:700;color:#3f2155;margin:0 0 8px;line-height:1.3;word-wrap:break-word;overflow-wrap:break-word;\">Sleep data you won't find anywhere else</h2>\n    <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#666;margin:0;line-height:1.6;\">Swipe to explore three original UK sleep datasets.</p>\n  </div>\n \n  <!-- Clip wrapper — this is what stops the page body scrolling sideways -->\n  <div style=\"width:100%;overflow:hidden;\">\n \n    <!-- Scroll track — only this element scrolls -->\n    <div style=\"display:flex;overflow-x:scroll;scroll-snap-type:x mandatory;-webkit-overflow-scrolling:touch;gap:12px;padding:4px 20px 16px;scrollbar-width:none;-ms-overflow-style:none;width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;\">\n \n      <a href=\"/pages/uk-sleep-statistics\" style=\"display:block;text-decoration:none;background:#ffffff;border:1px solid #e0d8ea;border-radius:12px;padding:22px 18px;min-width:calc(82vw - 20px);max-width:300px;scroll-snap-align:start;flex-shrink:0;\">\n        <div style=\"font-size:10px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:0.07em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#7f68a0;margin-bottom:10px;\">UK Sleep Statistics 2026</div>\n        <div style=\"font-size:38px;font-weight:700;color:#3f2155;line-height:1;margin-bottom:8px;\">72%</div>\n        <div style=\"font-size:14px;font-weight:600;color:#1a1a1a;margin-bottom:8px;line-height:1.35;\">of Brits aren't getting enough sleep</div>\n        <div style=\"font-size:12px;color:#666;line-height:1.55;margin-bottom:16px;\">50+ facts about how Britain sleeps — insomnia rates, economic cost, regional differences, and more.</div>\n        <div style=\"display:flex;padding-top:12px;border-top:1px solid #e0d8ea;\">\n          <div style=\"flex:1;text-align:center;\">\n            <div style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:700;color:#3f2155;\">£40bn</div>\n            <div style=\"font-size:10px;color:#888;margin-top:2px;line-height:1.3;\">annual cost to UK economy</div>\n          </div>\n          <div style=\"flex:1;text-align:center;border-left:1px solid #e0d8ea;\">\n            <div style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:700;color:#3f2155;\">50+</div>\n            <div style=\"font-size:10px;color:#888;margin-top:2px;line-height:1.3;\">statistics with sources</div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n        <div style=\"margin-top:16px;font-size:13px;font-weight:600;color:#3f2155;\">Read the statistics →</div>\n      </a>\n \n      <a href=\"/pages/uk-sleeper-preferences\" style=\"display:block;text-decoration:none;background:#3f2155;border:1px solid #3f2155;border-radius:12px;padding:22px 18px;min-width:calc(82vw - 20px);max-width:300px;scroll-snap-align:start;flex-shrink:0;\">\n        <div style=\"font-size:10px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:0.07em;text-transform:uppercase;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.55);margin-bottom:10px;\">UK Sleeper Preferences 2026</div>\n        <div style=\"font-size:38px;font-weight:700;color:#ffffff;line-height:1;margin-bottom:8px;\">105,165</div>\n        <div style=\"font-size:14px;font-weight:600;color:#fff;margin-bottom:8px;line-height:1.35;\">UK mattress shoppers surveyed</div>\n        <div style=\"font-size:12px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.7);line-height:1.55;margin-bottom:16px;\">How UK sleepers actually sleep — firmness, sleep positions, temperature needs, and motion sensitivity.</div>\n        <div style=\"display:flex;padding-top:12px;border-top:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2);\">\n          <div style=\"flex:1;text-align:center;\">\n            <div style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:700;color:#fff;\">84%</div>\n            <div style=\"font-size:10px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.55);margin-top:2px;line-height:1.3;\">want temperature regulation</div>\n          </div>\n          <div style=\"flex:1;text-align:center;border-left:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2);\">\n            <div style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:700;color:#fff;\">77%</div>\n            <div style=\"font-size:10px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.55);margin-top:2px;line-height:1.3;\">report back pain</div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n        <div style=\"margin-top:16px;font-size:13px;font-weight:600;color:#fff;\">Explore the data →</div>\n      </a>\n \n      <a href=\"/pages/back-pain-mattress-data\" style=\"display:block;text-decoration:none;background:#ffffff;border:1px solid #e0d8ea;border-radius:12px;padding:22px 18px;min-width:calc(82vw - 20px);max-width:300px;scroll-snap-align:start;flex-shrink:0;\">\n        <div style=\"font-size:10px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:0.07em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#7f68a0;margin-bottom:10px;\">Back Pain & Mattresses 2026</div>\n        <div style=\"font-size:38px;font-weight:700;color:#3f2155;line-height:1;margin-bottom:8px;\">84.5%</div>\n        <div style=\"font-size:14px;font-weight:600;color:#1a1a1a;margin-bottom:8px;line-height:1.35;\">of firm mattress shoppers report back pain</div>\n        <div style=\"font-size:12px;color:#666;line-height:1.55;margin-bottom:16px;\">What 105,165 UK sleepers reveal about back pain, firmness, sleep position, and what actually helps.</div>\n        <div style=\"display:flex;padding-top:12px;border-top:1px solid #e0d8ea;\">\n          <div style=\"flex:1;text-align:center;\">\n            <div style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:700;color:#3f2155;\">77%</div>\n            <div style=\"font-size:10px;color:#888;margin-top:2px;line-height:1.3;\">report back pain overall</div>\n          </div>\n          <div style=\"flex:1;text-align:center;border-left:1px solid #e0d8ea;\">\n            <div style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:700;color:#3f2155;\">65.